        "symbolName": "SpineDB",
        "description": "Unified facade class that aggregates all runtime database operations for ArchSpine, including file tracking, symbol indexing, usage logging, violation recording, drift history, and batch commits. Instantiated by the governance engine core to interact with the persistent runtime database."
